h3. Problem Definition
Currently, the Task Report Macro allows you to specify a user whose tasks you wish to display, but you cannot display for {{currently logged in user}}

h3. Suggested Solution
Create an option to show for currently logged in user, by passing the current user as a parameter to the macro
 
h3. Workaround 
Users can view their own current tasks in their Confluence Profile.

